			i also love to design things - software working is one thing, but in my opinion it should also look good and be fun to use. <a class="underline underline-offset-4   transition-all hover:font-extrabold hover:underline-offset-8 decoration-wavy hover:text-yellow">tactile design</a> is one way i achieve this.

			i'm good with python, astro, and godot, but i can pick up new things fairly quickly. currently, i'm procrastinating on learning rust and svelte.

			away from coding, I love to game (come find me on the hack club minecraft server!), read books, write about stuff (i'd love to write a book some day), pat my cats, make music, draw (kinda bad) pixel art, play retro video games, rock climb, snowboard, run and play D&D, and watch anime.

