			i've helped with design for the former <a href="https://github.com/thepurplebubble" class="underline underline-offset-4   transition-all hover:font-extrabold hover:underline-offset-8 decoration-wavy hover:text-mauve">Purple Bubble</a> as well.

			find my projects <a href="projects" class="underline underline-offset-4   transition-all hover:font-extrabold hover:underline-offset-8 decoration-wavy hover:text-blue">here</a>, play me and my friends' games on <a href="https://the-dimaverse.itch.io/" class="underline underline-offset-4   transition-all hover:font-extrabold hover:underline-offset-8 decoration-wavy hover:text-red">itch.io</a>, check out occasional project updates on my <a href="https://scrapbook.hackclub.com">hack club scrapbook</a>, and listen to me yap about various things on my <a href="https://social.dino.icu/@hex4" class="underline underline-offset-4   transition-all hover:font-extrabold hover:underline-offset-8 decoration-wavy hover:text-blue">mastodon.</a>

